The Clippings Series, 1983-1996,consists of photocopies of newspaper articles pertaining to LGHP activities and/or members. Most of the clippings originally appeared in the Durham Herald-Sun; the Raleigh News and Observer;
The Independent (an alternative newspaper based in Durham); and also in The Front Page,
The Newsletter, and Q-Notes ( gay and/or lesbian newspapers based in Raleigh, Durham, and Charlotte, respectively).

